data.title: Nexus Nexus Character Directory [Archive]
data.meta_description:
What is this place? Here is the place where aspiring Nexites post their characters, for easy reference. That way, you don't have to describe them every single time they appear! 
What is Nexus? Well, that's a question that can be better answered by the OoC thread. 
 
Below is a suggested format for character pages, but you can choose to format them however you want. I'm not you boss. 
 
CHARACTER NAME 
(use color of speech) 
 
Aliases: Sometimes people go by different names, be they secret
